pageContext.claim: “His name is Terrence Williams. I look -- and I look and I said, "Well, you know, the way you look…" And the first thing I look is, how many followers does he have? And he had like 700,000 followers.”
pageContext.analysis: Terrence K. Williams is a comedian who tweeted a conspiracy theory suggesting Bill Clinton had Jeffrey Epstein murdered. (Epstein committed suicide, officials determined.) Trump retweeted that. Just because someone has 700,000 Twitter does not mean that they are "respected."
